function v(t,n,r){return r===n?1:1-(t-n)/(r-n)}function u(t,n,r){return r===n?1:(t-n)/(r-n)}function x(t){if(t.length===0)return{cheapest:null,bestRated:null,bestValue:null,all:[]};let n=t.map(e=>e.price.total),r=t.map(e=>e.rating??0),o=t.map(e=>e.reviewCount),s=Math.min(...n),g=Math.max(...n),m=Math.min(...r),b=Math.max(...r),p=Math.min(...o),T=Math.max(...o),i=t.map(e=>({tour:e,score:v(e.price.total,s,g)*.4+u(e.rating??0,m,b)*.35+u(e.reviewCount,p,T)*.25}));i.sort((e,a)=>a.score-e.score);let l=t.filter(e=>e.rating!==null&&e.rating>=4),h=(l.length>0?l:t).reduce((e,a)=>a.price.total<e.price.total?a:e),c=t.filter(e=>e.reviewCount>=5&&e.rating!==null),d=(c.length>0?c:t).reduce((e,a)=>{let f=a.rating??0,C=e.rating??0;return f>C?a:e}),R=i[0].tour;return{cheapest:h,bestRated:d,bestValue:R,all:i.map(e=>e.tour)}}export{x as a};
